ity","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 4, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"'Uthman ibn Abi al-\u2018As reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cGabriel, upon him be peace, has come and commanded me to put this verse in this place, in this chapter: Verily, Allah has commanded justice and excellence and giving to relatives, and He has\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5609,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/27\/fitnah-hiyat-al-dunya-nisa-israil\/","url_meta":{"origin":34725,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Fitnah: Beware temptations of the worldly life","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 27, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe world is sweet and green. Verily, Allah will make you successors in it to see how you will behave. Beware of the world and beware of women. Verily, the first trial of the children\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":42790,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/03\/08\/zakariya-carpenter\/","url_meta":{"origin":34725,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Zakariya: Prophet Zechariah was a carpenter","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 8, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \